# Drafted SWR Font Characters

Based on the image provided, here is a visual draft in the project's standard `fonts*.txt` format for the missing characters needed for the SWR platform widget. 

## Large Platform Number Font

The platform number (such as "8") is significantly larger than any other element on the board, spanning the equivalent of two full service rows (approximately 15–16 pixels in height and 9-10 columns wide).

```text
Font: SWRPlatformNumberHuge
Glyph count: 1
b0: 3, b1: 2

Character U+0038 (Char: '8')
Width: 11, Height: 16, X-Offset: 0, Y-Offset: 2, dX: 13
